            single-page-apps, server-rendered apps, pre-rendered apps, PWA apps; sometimes with a framework, sometimes without.
            JavaScript has a great community and modern dev tooling that sets a pretty high bar.
        </p>
        <p>
            I also write Node.js back-ends, primarly with Express. I've become very experienced at creating modern API-first apps
            using REST conventions. My experience with ETL and data warehousing makes designing app data models a joy.
